N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 201.8 - Marketing and product research

State Regulations

The commissioner is hereby authorized to contract with any
person or persons, including the New York Apple Association, Inc., to carry on
or cause to be carried on apple marketing and/or product research and to expend
any available monies for such purpose. Notes
